.TH "nvme_dump_config" 9 "nvme_dump_config" "March 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_dump_config \- Print the JSON configuration
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" nvme_dump_config
.BI "(struct nvme_global_ctx *ctx "  ","
.BI "int fd "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
\fIstruct nvme_global_ctx\fP object
.IP "fd" 12
File descriptor to write the JSON configuration.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Writes the current contents of the JSON configuration
to the file descriptor fd.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, or negative error code otherwise.
